====Mexico====
[[Bernal Díaz]] recounted that, after landing on the [[Veracruz]] coast, they came across a temple dedicated to [[Tezcatlipoca]]. ''"That day they had sacrificed two boys, cutting open their chests and offering their blood and hearts to that accursed idol"''.<ref>{{Cite book
