==Modern times==

Infanticide has become less common in the [[Western world]].  The frequency has been estimated to be approximately 1 in 3000-5000 children of all ages <ref>Putkonen, Amon, Almiron, Cederwall, Eronen, Klier, Kjelsberg, Weizmann-Henelius (2009). Filicide in Austria and Finland - A register-based study on all filicide cases in Austria and Finland 1995-2005. BMC Psychiatry. 9:74.</ref> and 2.1 per 100,000 newborns per year.<ref>{{cite journal
